g.title: j4230829024
g.text: I spilled bubble tea on my PC pls tell me you got this message so I know everything works

g.title: j3784476909
g.text: omg thank all the gods. Amir would never have let me live that down

g.title: j2847325746
g.text: What kind of tea did you say it was?

g.title: j1745599493
g.text: And just how did you spill tea all over your PC?

g.title: j3253341311
g.text: bubble tea! it's a milky tea with chewy little tapioca pearls

g.title: j1122353768
g.text: ok don't make fun of me

g.title: j1156625596
g.text: So little of what you just said made sense to me, but I trust your taste.

g.title: j1968507388
g.text: I didn't have room on my desk so I sat my drink on the tower. then I was settling in, getting comfy

g.title: j1252046055
g.text: You seem upset. Is it something I said?

g.title: j3853354043
g.text: when I crossed my legs, my knee hit the bubble tea and BAM. Tea EVERYWHERE. Not a drop left in the cup!

g.title: j1050490600
g.text: Do you still have a few sips left at least?

g.title: j215219908
g.text: And this stuff nearly broke your PC?

g.title: j3180378202
g.text: The weirdest part of that story was when you sat cross-legged at a computer desk.

g.title: j847418142
g.text: I'm having a really hard time not making fun of you right now.

g.title: j952802046
g.text: I'll spare you the lecture about caring for your electronics.

g.title: j2540078503
g.text: I didn't love being called boring.

g.title: j3202909204
g.text: Oh. I really didn't mean anything by it.

g.title: j2009139905
g.text: pity meee! I only got like one sip and bubble tea's tough to come by around here!

g.title: j3104152563
g.text: No chance of getting another tea from wherever you got that one then?

g.title: j739355525
g.text: Okay, fair enough. That sucks. Silver lining is you didn't break anything though, right?

g.title: j2090016171
g.text: Honest. I'm sorry I upset you.

g.title: j371757787
g.text: You're not boring, Aoi. I just thought I was being clever.

g.title: j2786091478
g.text: If you were really boring, I wouldn't be talking to you.

g.title: j2721118161
g.text: I make it myself. gotta venture into scaldraville to find the ingredients tho

g.title: j4217503126
g.text: I do love a silver lining ^_^

g.title: j2290010234
g.text: It seems the jury's convinced by your defense

g.title: j987205383
g.text: Hey, that's not so bad. I hear Scaldraville's beautiful this time of year.

g.title: j3583859190
g.text: You must really like tea if you go to all that trouble.

g.title: j305993852
g.text: And we don't even have to tell Amir.

g.title: j1168222173
g.text: and grants you a fresh start

g.title: j3318286974
g.text: a little side quest never hurts! err... rarely hurts.

g.title: j2858047830
g.text: knew I could count on u

g.title: j4192432798
g.text: oh yah nothing beats that efervon smell in the air

g.title: j2959735379
g.text: nothing will stop me from treating myself ^_^

g.title: j2544801219
g.text: thank goodness ur so good at keeping secrets

g.title: j377657138
g.text: Oh, I see Aoi's emoticons are back. I think that's a good sign.

g.title: j4004092797
g.text: Looks like there was a little damage after all.

g.title: j1415620241
g.text: I think you'd better talk to Amir about fixing that.

g.title: j1875470911
g.text: I don't think typing is good for the keyboard at this point.

g.title: j258867459
g.text: I'd ask if you're okay over there but... it looks like replying will be difficult either way.

g.title: j250861882
g.text: Did Lettie's rats walk all over your keyboard or was that bubble tea damage?

g.title: j2476681543
g.text: I simply separated the metal in the keyboard from the liquid (and tapioca) then rebuilt it ^_^ good as new!

g.title: j4109410244
g.text: Wow you did that quickly too.

g.title: j3619624643
g.text: Damn, your powers are no joke.

g.title: j4062276547
g.text: I'm surprised you didn't think of that sooner.

g.title: j2858280593
g.text: yah sooo I'm totally gonna go brag to Amir
